Understand the Goal of Data Modeling

Instead of keeping everything in one big table, we split it into:

Fact Table → Transaction data (Sales)

Dimension Tables → descriptive information

This improves:

Performance

Data analysis

DAX calculations

2️ Identify Fact and Dimension Columns
FACT TABLE (Sales Transactions)

This table contains numeric measures.

FactSales

OrderID	OrderDate	ShipDate	CustomerID	ProductID	Sales	Quantity	Discount	Profit
DIMENSION TABLES
1️⃣ DimCustomer
CustomerID	CustomerName	Segment
2️⃣ DimProduct
ProductID	ProductName	Category	SubCategory
3️⃣ DimLocation
PostalCode	City	State	Country	Region
4️⃣ DimShipMode
ShipMode
5️⃣ DimDate (Calendar Table)
Date	Year	Quarter	Month	MonthName

Used for:

Order Date analysis

Time intelligence

