8️⃣ Create DAX Measures

In FactSales table.

Total Sales
Total Sales :=
SUM(FactSales[Sales])
Total Profit
Total Profit :=
SUM(FactSales[Profit])
Total Quantity
Total Quantity :=
SUM(FactSales[Quantity])
Profit Margin
Profit Margin :=
DIVIDE([Total Profit],[Total Sales])
Average Discount
Avg Discount :=
AVERAGE(FactSales[Discount])
